title: Le Mcdooby
author: Maximumfame
pages:
#- Mcdooby, your truly a chill dude. You may steal my cows, you may pillage my village, you may kill me outside a coty. but you're still a cool guy to have in mumble. You are one lovable asshole, I used to not like you for killing me, but even I couldn't res
#- ist the mcdoobys. Stay cool and keep playing, we love to have you around. Just don't yolo too hard like you did last time and try not to get 420 overload.
